            "title": "Southwest Gas Holdings priced the secondary public offering of Centuri Holdings Common Stock on Aug 7, 2025.",
            "id": "90e5ff5e-8067-4225-b375-edb4ed11f42b",
            "description": "Southwest Gas Holdings, Inc. revealed today the pricing details of an underwritten secondary public offering of Centuri Holdings, Inc. common stock. This offering involves Centuri common stock traded on the NYSE under the symbol CTRI. The announcement regarding this move was made on August 7, 2025, in Las Vegas. Southwest Gas Holdings, listed as SWX on the NYSE, is facilitating this offering. The specifics such as the exact number of shares offered and the pricing details were not disclosed in the provided excerpt.",
